## Validation Status
- Test suite was run and reported passing after syntax/type fixes.
- Documentation was aligned to reflect summary mode and dual-note refs.

## Review Findings (Open)
- **P1:** Summary generation prompt does not include transcript content, risking ungrounded summaries.
- **P2:** Dual-note writes are non-atomic; if full-audit write fails after summary write, notes can become inconsistent.

## Current State
Feature is implemented and documented, but the two review findings above indicate functional risk that should be addressed next.
